{"tid":52384,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"求好心人領養一隻三色貓","createTime":"2016-12-24T04:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T18:07:33.000Z","uid":67836,"like":0,"dislike":91,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ca87da10089b95931d9cc400502eaadee825d01","tid":52384,"uid":67836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:36:11.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">隻貓一歲左右 三色平日好乖<br />\n雖然中意叫 但係你摸下佢就無事<br />\n朋友因為突如其來有左小朋<br />\n友家人又反對養貓怕有影響<br />\n所以希望有個有心人可以幫<br />\n手最好有養過貓或者依家有養緊</div><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/123128_94cd376f705b89c60d4117087b565220.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F123128_94cd376f705b89c60d4117087b565220.jpg&h=049297aa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e8617k4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe8617k4.jpg&h=47d4b759&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/123129_81075bf94b9780287698f8b69e2a3455.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F123129_81075bf94b9780287698f8b69e2a3455.jpg&h=053f4627&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M2p9x25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM2p9x25.jpg&h=9bc1ef5a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/et1V3K5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fet1V3K5.jpg&h=2a24d77a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聯絡方法：97088987<br />\n利申：我的朋友不是我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44eb52f8f5e6e0236f7efdd6a9c08abecb83e581","tid":52384,"uid":754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:39:28.000Z","msg":"真係有心養嘅 屋企家人點反對都會堅持<br />\n而唔係話俾人就俾人<br />\n<br />\n希望貓仔搵到個好歸宿"},{"pid":"966720158ba02aef19b710c381db99fa0c380381","tid":52384,"uid":28626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:40:27.000Z","msg":"幫推.."},{"pid":"20fdc8bac20b84015a6b54117fe109d792872515","tid":52384,"uid":22291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:40:32.000Z","msg":"仲以為養貓狗會影響小朋友呢d封建家庭係邊到搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eedcbb0850de97ef0bf4ed2413f05d144553d2e","tid":52384,"uid":68478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:42:06.000Z","msg":"有小朋友？個小朋友陀得穩+出到世先講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e1300c68dab815170541e5a1ba2e44240ee713","tid":52384,"uid":67836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:42:42.000Z","msg":"佢地家人話有小朋友近得貓多（甩毛）<br />\n會有鼻敏感"},{"pid":"6f69aa8c07c89b7a257e9df2ff315521620adf33","tid":52384,"uid":37758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:44:22.000Z","msg":"留名睇比人插到反皮"},{"pid":"3333e71a0c703c619833d1417ad44367902c640e","tid":52384,"uid":50892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:44:59.000Z","msg":"養貓養狗先會減低小朋友有敏感嘅情況呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab14d4088dd35f1715d34e89a72b5a3f924b5c2c","tid":52384,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:45:07.000Z","msg":"你朋友咁on9咪學人生啦, 隻貓1歲即係最多養左1年, 如果係plan左生仔又要養貓即頭係雙重仆街"},{"pid":"b4fd0ea3eeed738d96cbecd9d8e13918d79d8952","tid":52384,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:47:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢地家人話有小朋友近得貓多（甩毛）<br />\n會有鼻敏感</blockquote><br />\n有貓狗嘅家庭小朋友鼻敏感機會低啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自細住無菌屋個啲先最易出事, 外面一街都係菌同塵, 邊樣唔1毒過啲貓毛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個bb上世唔知做錯咩先投胎到一個咁on9嘅家庭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af68be291e2450eb553b542b7e95bc6bb01717e3","tid":52384,"uid":31257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:47:50.000Z","msg":"係香港呼吸都有鼻敏感啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非佢住郊外姐"},{"pid":"7def850b45a42780dfc53d45be3214ce57806b65","tid":52384,"uid":57695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:48:01.000Z","msg":"以為樓主講成日叫人返高登個位會然"},{"pid":"99c0275ddf58b3a16059bc2b103caa9ed436f3e2","tid":52384,"uid":35818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:50:14.000Z","msg":"咁靚都唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想養"},{"pid":"55c8da898ef5cc8a9889f9fa2efb4430151fab94","tid":52384,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:52:14.000Z","msg":"你朋友真扑街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5fdca95df0479b6100a6697a5f4dcfcfdfd89c","tid":52384,"uid":64585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:52:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://pets.feel.hk/article/detail?conCatID=382&amp;contentID=12672\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpets.feel.hk%2Farticle%2Fdetail%3FconCatID%3D382%26contentID%3D12672&d=F015TIYXqsL6BEeyf7lUgQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=c055bbe8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pets.feel.hk/article/detail?conCatID=382&amp;contentID=12672</a><br />\n<br />\n睇你對隻貓有冇感情，願意付出幾多<br />\n未養就懶有熱誠，養左就做多少少都厭煩<br />\n一句唔要就送走佢地一生<br />\n唔好再搵籍口啦，有冇鼻敏感睇你點預防<br />\n要做棄養撚就索性個b都咪撚養喇，呢種人個責任心同埋判斷力太低喇，養咩都唔適合<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6711f5470fbfc1ca50835762ef8cf472cb5972b9","tid":52384,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:01:23.000Z","msg":"根本就無關係<br />\n唔好聽d 八婆亂講啦<br />\n<br />\n你去教下你朋友<br />\n返去趕d 家人走<br />\n放棄佢地就啱"},{"pid":"01ca482b070ab20e8c6dba9e55429e8d818fc349","tid":52384,"uid":34331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:01:58.000Z","msg":"on9抗體係可以培養<br />\n我細個氣管敏感鼻敏感都照養<br />\n依加無病無痛<br />\n日日同隻貓訓<br />\n你啲朋友真係好無知<br />\n日日幫你地叫外賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc0f2c7e6deb9a8b5fd6a557b2bf769161dfad1","tid":52384,"uid":2986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:03:26.000Z","msg":"無知真係好撚恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c6e5c503c3095494e512e1473d56c6937ccf273","tid":52384,"uid":5011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:03:34.000Z","msg":"垃圾又因爲大肚棄養，根本人貓就可以共存，自己做好衛生清潔就得。好多人都有bb同時養貓<br />\n<br />\n總之棄養就準備比人咒死啦，唔好同我講咩唔係人人都視貓&gt;屋企人，你帶得佢番屋企，就有責任照顧佢一生，唔係你就一開始唔好養！垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb83c31e845c461be6cad229d2f725bf02f17f7f","tid":52384,"uid":30379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:05:59.000Z","msg":"咁仆街嘅主人,跟住都唔會好,希望搵到好嘅主人家"},{"pid":"a253bc1d17aa330a579b601745779edb0cc7d295","tid":52384,"uid":53652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:07:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係呢d藉口 睇下咩係immunisation 先啦"},{"pid":"8cd8d2f2257ecc9f68fc868c5c077b1a1e73c6d5","tid":52384,"uid":5011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:08:36.000Z","msg":"有鼻敏感要有就會有，唔好咩都賴貓。如果因為貓毛搞到鼻敏感，根本係養果個人既問題，日日吸塵抹地，幫貓梳走死毛，我就唔信仲會有咁多貓毛。呢啲你養得都應該一早知"},{"pid":"86ea8ef84bfbcd453b3a951e9e97451a15933b00","tid":52384,"uid":67893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:08:49.000Z","msg":"我表姐大肚生女全程養貓都冇事<br />\n注意乾淨衛生就得<br />\n棄養寧捨多籍口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f25864b41b6f5454526b190893601d45865fcfa9","tid":52384,"uid":4326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:13:21.000Z","msg":"戇鳩<br />\n有主人幫你睇住個b 呀"},{"